data.description: Take in the scenic view of beautiful farms on your drive to 26 Hilburn Rd. This house offers 5 bedrooms, 2 of which can be easily made into one large room. The owner has created these 2 bedrooms where the partitioned wall can be easily disassembled and made into one large room. Use your imagination and convert these two bedrooms into a large den, man-cave or she-shed, a playroom, or home gym. Homeowners are willing to disassemble walls to make this home fit your needs and make your move easier. The large metal building out back is only a year old, measures 24x50x12, and can hold up to 6 cars. Think of all the creative uses this building can provide. Enjoy your beverage of choice on the porches as you watch the sunset over the surrounding farmland. Call today to schedule your appointment. Roof: 2019Back Deck: 2019Carport: 2019Heat Pump and Air Conditioner: 2016Metal Building 24x50: 2022Windows: 2018 Bone Dry Crawl Space: 2022: removed ground debris/insulation, Installed 10 mil. seal vents, electrician, condensation pump, drain, sprayed joist and subfloor sanitizer, installed industrial grade dehumidifier, condensation pump and drained to daylight.
